            </div>
            <img
              width="496"
              class="absolute left-[50%] top-[50%] z-[1] max-w-[496px] translate-x-[-50%] translate-y-[-50%] opacity-30 transition-all group-hover:left-[70%] group-hover:opacity-70 group-hover:blur-[6px]"
              src="/game-project/optimized/card-bg.webp"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-4 pt-[16px]">
          <div
            class="card-gradient group relative min-h-[350px] w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[12px] bg-cover bg-center p-6 transition-all"
            style="background-color: #1F2324;"
          >
            <div
              class="app-text-gradient-bg z-[2] max-w-[419px] font-Oxanium text-[32px] font-medium uppercase leading-[120%] group-hover:hidden group-hover:bg-none"
            >
              Fair in-game economy
            </div>
            <div
              class="z-[2] hidden max-w-[419px] font-Oxanium text-[32px] font-medium uppercase leading-[120%] group-hover:block group-hover:bg-none"
            >
              Fair in-game economy
            </div>
            <div class="z-[2] mt-6 max-w-[510px]">
              We always think about the fairness of all processes on the
