            >
              Producing centre
            </div>
            <div
              class="z-[2] hidden max-w-[349px] font-Oxanium text-[32px] font-medium uppercase leading-[120%] group-hover:block group-hover:bg-none"
            >
              Producing centre
            </div>
            <div class="z-[2] mt-6 max-w-[515px]">
              We are always happy to see new projects on our platform, so we
              provide the best methods to promote your projects
            </div>
            <img
              width="496"
              class="absolute left-[50%] top-[50%] z-[1] max-w-[496px] translate-x-[-50%] translate-y-[-50%] opacity-30 transition-all group-hover:left-[70%] group-hover:opacity-70 group-hover:blur-[6px]"
              src="/game-project/optimized/card-bg.webp"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- our mission -->
    <section>
      <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto mt-[130px] max-w-[1520px]">
        <div class="font-Oxanium text-[64px] font-medium uppercase">
          Our mission
        </div>
        <div class="flex">
          <div class="pt-12 text-[40px] leading-[120%]">
            <span class="text-[#FD4E07]"
              >To promote blockchain technologies and empower users to select
              games tailored to their preferences.</span
            >
            Our platform features the most engaging games with innovative and equitable
            reward systems
            <div class="mt-9 text-[16px] leading-[120%]">
              To make BIZZON not just one of the most attractive and popular
              platforms for a narrow crypto audience, but also to attract a
              broad mass of users unfamiliar with the cryptocurrency world in
              order to introduce them the most fast growing industry of our
              time. To teach them how to understand and use blockchain solutions
              based on the most widespread and at the same time the simplest
              application - <span class="app-text-gradient-bg"
                >gamification</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
          <img
            width="729"
            class="max-w-[729px]"
            src="/game-project/optimized/mission-image.webp"
            alt=""
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <!-- game world -->
    <section class="mt-[150px] overflow-hidden">
      <div class="text-center font-Oxanium text-[48px] font-medium uppercase">
        Game World
      </div>
      <div class="mt-[48px] flex animate-walk">
        <img src="/game-project/optimized/game-landing-1.webp" alt="" />
        <img src="/game-project/optimized/game-landing-2.webp" alt="" />
        <img src="/game-project/optimized/game-landing-3.webp" alt="" />
